    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you\u2014it is in incredible, showroom-level shape! It\u2019s been totally babied since day one, kept tucked away in the garage, and honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You've got to see this beauty in person to believe how clean it is\u2014swing by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
