    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional example of the E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the M-Variable differential. The chassis integrity is superlative, with zero subframe fatigue and a factory-spec suspension geometry maintained via Bilstein B16 coilovers. The Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible orange peel or clear coat failure. A true collector-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Clean title. No accidents. Low mileage. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
