    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality specimen. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All technological features, including the advanced driver assistance systems and the high-fidelity audio suite, operate with precision. Mechanically, this car is superlative. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy at authorized service centers, and I have a complete, organized binder of every service receipt since day one. With remarkably low mileage and a documented history of being adult-driven and meticulously cared for, this is arguably the finest example currently available on the market.",
