      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. It\u2019s super rare to find one this clean. If you want a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
